OL,6,FA mother whose son was left brain
OL,7,Fdamaged after contracting whooping
OL,8,Fcough as a baby is urging pregnant
OL,9,Fwomen to get vaccinated.
OL,11,FSpike Ray from Henfield, West Sussex,
OL,12,Fspent weeks in hospital after
OL,13,Fdeveloping whooping cough at 11 days
OL,14,Fold.
OL,16,FHis mother, Susan, photographed him
OL,17,Fevery day after doctors warned that
OL,18,Feach day could be his last.
