OL,6,FSusan Ray, Spike's mother, said: "I
OL,7,Fwas a staff nurse. For me, I've seen
OL,8,Flots of medical machinery, but when
OL,9,Fit's your own child, it takes on a
OL,10,Fwhole new level.
OL,12,F"I don't think you can process it, you
OL,13,Fkind of get swept along. It was the
OL,14,Fmost fearful time of our lives."
OL,16,FMore than 7,500 cases of whooping
OL,17,Fcough have already been recorded in
OL,18,F2024, with 1,500 of those in the South
OL,19,FEast.
