OL,4,Cvaccine for 'killer' whooping cough
OL,6,FPregnant women are now urged to get
OL,7,Fvaccinated as whooping cough cases are
OL,8,Fincreasing.
OL,10,FSusan said: "If I could turn back the
OL,11,Fclock, I would be running to my GP to
OL,12,Fget that vaccine done. It's not only a
OL,13,Fcough, it's a killer.
OL,15,F"Look at the damage that's been done
OL,16,Fand this is what we have to deal with
OL,17,Fevery single day."
OL,19,FDespite being under regular
OL,20,Fobservation from doctors, Spike lives
OL,21,Fevery day positively.
